data.description: Beautiful, 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home located in desirable Lindberg Village. There is so much space to entertain with a living room, dining room, AND a large family room with gas fireplace which opens to the eat-in kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances, ceramic tile, walk-in pantry, and breakfast bar. Enormous master bedroom with huge walk-in closet and lovely en suite with dual vanity, jacuzzi tub and separate shower. Three generously sized bedrooms with great closet space, spacious loft living area, and second floor laundry room! This house is ready for you to personalize with a $10,000 flooring credit payable at closing. Large, privacy-fenced backyard with paver patio, three car garage, and convenient to Purdue University.
